<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="apply-v">apply <strong><em>v</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /ə'plaɪ/    美 /ə'plaɪ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>申请</strong></h4>
<p>to make a formal request, usually in writing：</p>
<ul>
<li>apply for sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>apply for a job / passport / visa
申请工作/护照/签证</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I am writing to apply for the post of volunteer for our school English association.
我写信申请我们学校英语协会志愿者这个职位。</p><footer>2018 浙江书面表达</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>apply to sb / sth (for sth):</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>apply to a company / university
向公司/大学申请</p></div>

<ul>
<li>apply to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He applied to study composition with the well-known musician.
他申请跟这位著名音乐家学习作曲。</p><footer>2013 山东</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>运用；应用；使用：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We had to write a paper on how we plan to <strong>apply</strong> what we would learn in class to our future professions and to our lives<strong>to_3</strong<strong>to_4</strong>
我们必须写一篇论文，论述我们如何计划将我们课堂上所学到的运用到将来的工作和生活中去。</p><footer>2018 全国改</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The new technology was <strong>applied to</strong> farming.
这项新技术被应用于农业。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>[不用于进行时] (对…) 适用；(对…) 有效：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If the constitution said that all people were free and equal, then she thought it should <strong>apply to</strong> her.
如果这部宪法称所有人都是自由和平等的，那么她认为这也应适用于自己。</p><footer>2014 山东</footer></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>涂；敷：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Apply</strong> the cream evenly <strong>to</strong> your face and neck.
将乳霜均匀地涂抹于面部和颈部。</p></div>

<h4 id="5">5.<strong>努力；使专注于：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Recently, he has <strong>applied himself to</strong> his studies.
近来，他专心学习。</p></div>

<h4 id="6">6.<strong>手压；脚踩：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>apply the brakes
踩刹车</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He slowed the bleeding by <strong>applying pressure</strong> to the wounds.
他按住伤口以减少流血。</p><footer>人教⑤ – 5</footer></div></div>